### 2.2 — Voice Message Pipeline
**Priority:** 🟡 IMPORTANT  
**Why:** Bangladeshi customers frequently send voice messages.  
Currently these are ignored (black box).  
**Impact:** New capability. Significant UX improvement.

#### What needs to happen:
1. Detect audio attachment in webhook (`audio`, `voice` type)
2. Download m4a/mp4 file from Facebook CDN
3. Send to ElevenLabs Scribe API (3.1% WER on Bangla)
4. Inject transcription as `[Voice Message]: {text}` into conversation
5. Agent responds normally to transcribed text

#### Files to create/modify:
- `lib/voice/transcribe.ts` — ElevenLabs Scribe integration
- `app/api/webhooks/facebook/route.ts` — detect audio attachment type
- `lib/conversation/orchestrator.ts` — inject transcription into message

