### 3.2 — Multi-Model Strategy (Claude Haiku for Action Pass)
**Priority:** 🟢 OPTIMIZATION  
**Why:** Research shows Claude 3.5 Haiku has superior instruction  
following for complex tool calls vs GPT-4o-mini.

#### What needs to happen:
- Pass 1 (Reasoning): Keep GPT-4o-mini (cheap, fast)
- Pass 2 (Action/Tools): Try Claude 3.5 Haiku (better tool reliability)
- A/B test for 1 week, compare hallucination rate

#### Note:
Do NOT implement until Phase 1 and 2 are complete and stable.  
This is an experiment, not a guaranteed improvement.

